gov.nih.nlm.ling.process

Interface TermAnnotator

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    IndicatorAnnotator

    public interface TermAnnotator
    An interface for term annotator modules. Each term annotator is provided with a Document object, a Properties where term annotator properties can be read from. The results are returned as a map of SpanList/Term key/value pairs.
    Author:
    Halil Kilicoglu
